1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 30-A MRSA ยง3112 is enacted to read:
3 ยง3112. Placement of noncitizens by the State
4 1. Noncitizen; defined. As used in this section, unless the context otherwise indicates,
5 "noncitizen" has the same meaning as in Title 22, section 4099-I, subsection 1, paragraph
6 E.
7 2. Placement of noncitizens by the State. The State may not place a noncitizen within
8 a municipality without prior authorization from the municipality. A municipality may
9 designate the number of noncitizens the State is allowed to place within that municipality,
10 and the State may not exceed the number of noncitizens designated by the municipality.
11 SUMMARY
1122 This bill prohibits the State from placing noncitizens within a municipality without the
1133 municipality's prior authorization and allows the municipality to limit the number of
1144 noncitizens the State places within the municipality.
